		<p><a href="http://www.infoq.com/presentations/We-Really-Dont-Know-How-To-Compute" title="Sussman talk" rel="nofollow">&#8220;We Really Don&#8217;t Know How To Compute!&#8221;</a> is a very interesting talk.</p>

		<div class="reply">
		<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='/?p=55&#038;replytocom=6730#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-6730", "6730", "respond", "55")'>Reply</a>		</div>
